Here are some clear, practical benefits of your travel portal:

* Role-based access control ensures only the right users can view or approve requests
* User-specific data visibility keeps information secure and relevant
* Structured approval workflow eliminates confusion and manual follow-ups
* Faster approval process with clearly defined stages and responsibilities
* Real-time tracking of request status from creation to completion
* Controlled edit permissions (only BM can edit at the right stage) prevents data misuse
* Improved transparency with complete visibility of the approval flow
* Audit-friendly design with timestamps and workflow history
* Reusable and scalable architecture for future enhancements (like BPM tools)
* Clean and intuitive UI improves user experience and reduces errors
